{"tid":1483391,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"幫手填個問卷，幫助我早日可以出黎再抗戰","createTime":"2019-08-18T11:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T03:45:43.000Z","uid":269096,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"04084c7d81730538e3e1c4823b1a666ff1123e8c","tid":1483391,"uid":269096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:42:10.000Z","msg":"話說小妹已經抗爭左好耐，無奈我又有dissertation在身，係打工抗爭入面仲要sip時間寫paper真係好想喊，仲諗住想休學一陣打好場仗先，但一諗到係長期戰又唔想被篇paper阻住哂，所以決定點都死埋佢出黎。<br />\n<br />\n呢排大家時間都好寶貴，但如果阻你5分鐘，可以解決困擾我寫完FYP呢個困難，唔知你肯唔肯為我填份，再share 出去呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 為左答謝大家，我收集完之後，會搞個抽獎多謝大家，可以拎番 $200 coupon (decathlon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />／starbucks／惠康) 任君選擇。 得 $200唔好意思，因為已課太多，又買gear，身上都冇咩錢咁制...<br />\n<br />\n打咁多野都只係希望你可以幫手填個問券<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：今日行完又要番屋企打文，真係好想同各位一齊係維園守到夜晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://survey.sogosurvey.com/survey.aspx?k=RQsQTYVPSsSsPsPsP&amp;lang=0&amp;data=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsurvey.sogosurvey.com%2Fsurvey.aspx%3Fk%3DRQsQTYVPSsSsPsPsP%26lang%3D0%26data%3D&d=xzf4O3tGv54ZmzQe4QccrH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=897cc561\" target=\"_blank\">https://survey.sogosurvey.com/survey.aspx?k=RQsQTYVPSsSsPsPsP&amp;lang=0&amp;data=</a><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，決一不